About Us: BEGUR & PARTNERS (formerly known as ARA LAW), founded in 1996 is a dynamic first-generation law firm known for its creative and agile thinking,
commitment to its clients and the ability to provide sound and innovative solutions. Our INNOVATIVE approach coupled with the FOCUSSED ATTENTION helped
us emanate as a TRUSTED ADVISOR. Our commitment to excellence drives us to work in a more creative, collaborative and accountable manner that leverages the
expertise of our entire team and helps us fuel our clients’ vision by providing them the finest blueprint to spearhead their ideas into reality. Our Way of Life reflects
our WORK CULTURE. We firmly believe in nurturing a culture conducive to the holistic personal and professional growth and development of the Team, in turn
translating into the Firm’s success story. Our SUCCESS lies in seeing that our clients get quick, creative, pragmatic and cost-effective solutions that stand the test
of time. Our logo symbolizes the power of the INFINITE potential we possess to learn, contribute and grow.
